text: Five fat santas jumping in the snow
One fell off and bumped his toe
The elfs called the doctor and the doctor said,
"No more santas jumping in the snow!"
Four fat santas jumping in a snow
One fell off and bumped his toe
The elves called the doctor and the doctor said,
"No more santas jumping in the snow!"
Three fat santas jumping in a snow
One fell off and bumped his toe
The elves called the doctor and the doctor said,
"No more santas jumping in the snow!"
Two fat santas jumping in a snow
One fell off and bumped his toe
The elves called the doctor and the doctor said,
"No more santas jumping in the snow!"
One fat santas jumping in a snow
One fell off and bumped his toe
The elves called the doctor and the doctor said,
"Put those santas right to bed!"
